Package org.helmetsrequired.jacocotogo

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HelpMojo
    Display help information on jacocotogo-maven-plugin.
    Call mvn jacocotogo:help -Ddetail=true -Dgoal=<goal-name> to display parameter details.
    JaCoCoToGo
    JaCoCoToGo class.
    JaCoCoToGoBatchMojo
    Retrieves JaCoCo execution data from multiple sources, and optionally, merge the results.
    JaCoCoToGoJmxMojo
    Retrieves jacoco data from remote servers where the 'org.jacoco:type=Runtime MBean' is exposed via JMX
    JaCoCoToGoTcpMojo
    Retrieves jacoco data from remote servers where the jacoco javaagent is running with output=tcpserver
    Source
    Represents a single source for JaCoCo execution data.
